==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Mountain specter
<hw>Moun"tain spec"ter</hw>. <def>An optical phenomenon sometimes seen
on the summit of mountains (as on the Brocken) when the observer is
between the sun and a mass of cloud. The figures of the observer and
surrounding objects are seen projected on the cloud, greatly enlarged
and often encircled by rainbow colors.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>Webster 1913 Suppl.</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Mountain State</ent>⟦br⟧
